Several key players dominate the global plastic waste management market, providing a diverse range of services and solutions to address the growing challenge of plastic waste. Companies like Veolia, Suez, Waste Management Inc., and Clean Harbors are prominent players offering comprehensive waste management services from collection to recycling. Stericycle specializes in hazardous waste management, including plastic waste, while Republic Services Inc. focuses on sustainable waste solutions for various industries. Covanta Holding Corporation is known for its energy-from-waste facilities that convert plastic waste into clean energy. Remondis SE & Co. KG, Biffa, and Waste Connections are also key players contributing to the efficient management of plastic waste globally.

